rget=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532685\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104uhk1665703174125.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhk1665703174125.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/uhk1665703174125.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"uhk1665703174125\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The Uniface database connector interface is very stable and changes to it are\n      infrequent.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"uhk1665703174125__p_d131741e1_d131742e1_d131743e1\">The following table lists the major changes that connector developers should be aware of when updating existing connectors.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Changed and Obsolete Functionality</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__1\">Feature</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__2\">Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__3\">Explanation</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__4\">Uniface Release</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__1\">All connector requests, except for Logon, Logoff,\n                     Info Mode 0, Message, and Name table</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__2\"> Connector Requests</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__3\">New return status (<code class=\"ph codeph\">-9\n                        UIOSERR_LOGON_ERROR</code>  ). This indicates that the database connection\n                     has been lost. User-defined database connectors should be updated to handle\n                     this predefined Uniface error class. For more information, see the \"Error\n                     Handling\" topic.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__4\">Uniface 8.4.06 and Uniface 9.1.02</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__1\">Update</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__2\">Connector Request </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__3\">New return status (<code class=\"ph codeph\">-2\n                        UIOSERR_OCC_NOT_FOUND</code> ). This indicates that the specified record\n                     does not exist. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__4\">Uniface 8.2.02</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__1\">\n<span class=\"ph filepath\">uicc.h</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__2\">Header File</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__3\"> Renamed to <span class=\"ph filepath\">iccapi.h</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__4\">Uniface 8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">uxstring.h</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__2\">Header File</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__3\">Renamed to <span class=\"ph filepath\">unistr.h</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__4\">Uniface 8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">uiodef.h</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__2\">Header File</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__3\">Renamed to <span class=\"ph filepath\">unidbm.h</span></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__4\"> Uniface 8</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uiflst-&gt;type</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__2\"> Data Structure Field</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__3\"> Renamed and retyped to <code class=\"ph codeph\">unsigned short)\n                        uctrl-&gt;pack</code>. Its contents are compatible with Uniface\n                     V7.2.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__4\"> Uniface 7.2</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uctrl-&gt;uctrli</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__2\"> Data Structure Field</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__3\">Obsolete since Uniface 6. All references to this\n                     field can be replaced with the reference to <span class=\"ph filepath\">uctrl</span>\n                     itself.</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__4\">Uniface 7</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uloadcb()</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__2\">Service Function</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__3\">Obsolete since Uniface 6. All calls (address\n                     translations) to <code class=\"ph codeph\">uloadcb()</code> can be removed. For example:\n                           <p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">next = uloadcb(uctrl-&gt;uchfw)</code></p>\n<p class=\"p\">is now</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">next = uctrl-&gt;uchfw</code></p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"uhk1665703174125__table_d15737e1_d15738e1_d15739e1__entry__4\">Uniface 7</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/upy1665702977778.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Error Handling</a><p>Uniface provides an error handling mechanism that allows you to trap errors defined by Uniface, the connector, and the DBMS.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/azl1665702915888.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uctrl</a><p>Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532685\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532685\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Changed Functionality in the Database Connector Interface Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The Uniface database connector interface is very stable and changes to it are infrequent. The following table lists the major changes that connector developers should be aware of when updating existing connectors. Table 1. Changed and Obsolete Functionality Feature Type Explanation Uniface Release All connector requests, except for Logon, Logoff, Info Mode 0, Message, and Name table Connector Requests New return status ( -9 UIOSERR_LOGON_ERROR ). This indicates that the database connection has been lost. User-defined database connectors should be updated to handle this predefined Uniface error class. For more information, see the \"Error Handling\" topic. Uniface 8.4.06 and Uniface 9.1.02 Update Connector Request New return status ( -2 UIOSERR_OCC_NOT_FOUND ). This indicates that the specified record does not exist. Uniface 8.2.02 uicc.h Header File Renamed to iccapi.h Uniface 8 uxstring.h Header File Renamed to unistr.h Uniface 8 uiodef.h Header File Renamed to unidbm.h Uniface 8 uiflst->type Data Structure Field Renamed and retyped to unsigned short) uctrl->pack . Its contents are compatible with Uniface V7.2. Uniface 7.2 uctrl->uctrli Data Structure Field Obsolete since Uniface 6. All references to this field can be replaced with the reference to uctrl itself. Uniface 7 uloadcb() Service Function Obsolete since Uniface 6. All calls (address translations) to uloadcb() can be removed. For example: next = uloadcb(uctrl->uchfw) is now next = uctrl->uchfw Uniface 7 Related Links Error Handling Uniface provides an error handling mechanism that allows you to trap errors defined by Uniface, the connector, and the DBMS. uctrl Exchanges general information between Uniface and the connector, and describes a table. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}